# Post-Incident Review (PIR)

## Purpose
Convert incidents into organizational learning.

---

## Review Agenda
1. Incident summary
2. Timeline of events
3. Root cause (technical + process)
4. What worked well
5. What can be improved
6. Preventive actions

---

## Outputs
- Updated SOPs
- Infrastructure or configuration changes
- Training or communication improvements
- Vendor corrective actions

---

## Rule
No blame. Only improvement.
